### 2048

```
$ cd your 2048
$ git fetch origin
$ git checkout gh-pages
```
### Authors and Contributors
This is an fork of an existing repository created by Gabriele Cirulli(@gabrielecirulli). You can find his original game here:
https://github.com/gabrielecirulli/2048
My other projects and github page can be found at https://github.com/spunkpike. 
### Support or Contact
Having trouble with Pages? Check out the documentation at https://github.com/spunkpike or contact spunkpike@gmail.com and I'll try to help you sort it out.
